<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Thucydides, <i>The Peloponnesian War</i>, <a href="//en.wikisource.org/wiki/History_of_the_Peloponnesian_War/Book_6#6:42" class="extiw" title="s:History of the Peloponnesian War/Book 6">6.42</a>.</span></li>
